Saints will not be thus affronted, but level<lb/>
and discharge the Ordnance of his power<lb/>
                  <pb n="13"/>
                  <lb/>
against those that disclaim the Ordinances<lb/>
of his Grace. But I hope, through the <notvariant>pourings</notvariant><lb/>
out of the Spirit many shall be so wise<lb/>
