            <div>
               <head>The third Part of the<lb/>
NARRATIVE;<lb/>
Containing<lb/>
The <normalised orig="wonderfull" auto="true">wonderful</normalised> Recovery of this <normalised orig="Childe" auto="true">Child</normalised><lb/>
